data.description:
*SELLER OFFERING ASSISTANCE IN BUYER CLOSING COSTS!*
Spacious ranch-styled home nestled on 2.7 acres, featuring a thoughtful layout. 
The large kitchen boasts an open pantry and a convenient passthrough window to the living room. Designed for practical living, the primary bedroom is situated at one end, while the other two bedrooms occupy the opposite end. The dining area connects to the living room, creating an open atmosphere. This home also offers a full, unfinished, walkout basement and a breezeway linking the house to the oversized 2-car garage. Enjoy outdoor living on the back deck, surrounded by the tranquility of nature. Updates include a furnace and AC replaced in 2023, roof replacement in 2015 and includes a water softener and  pellet stove.
